20171229
* Moved from a version number, to a Revision ID (YEAR MONTH DATE)
* Patch script will auto-update itself once a new version is released.

Code Changes
* If no client is specified, "retail" is automatically used. - Thanks @Lykos
* If the "trollop" gem is is not installed, the script will install it for you. - Thanks @Lykos
* Moved the "[ OK ]" output on downloading a file to only display it _after_ the file has been downloaded.

